    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers generally to workmen and craftsmen who work with marble, including those who do any of quarrying, dressing, sculpting, mosaic, and masonry work.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
